{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Closely related to contemporary deep learning-based captioning are the tasks of paragraph captioning and video captioning.",
    "Paragraph image captioning is the challenge of generating a multi-sentence description of an image [61,62], whilst video captioning focuses on describing videos.",
    "Readers interested in video captioning are directed to the recent survey [63].Taxonomies of VQA are usually defined through the lens of the datasets used by the various tasks [43,44].",
    "Here we focus on 1) the standard VQA task of answering a ques-tion about an image, 2) the fact-based VQA (FVQA) task of answering questions that require external knowledge to answer, and 3) TextVQA, the task of answering questions that require the model to read text in the scene and combine it with visual data.",
    "Each of the various VQA tasks have their own set of speicalised datasets."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Paragraph image captioning is the challenge of generating a multi-sentence description of an image [61,62], whilst video captioning focuses on describing videos.",
